name: Baaddd Shirt or Ice Cream Candy Shirt
description:
The pink shirt is the BAADDD shirt, and the white is the ICE CREAM CANDY shirt. These are GILDAN shirts, hand silk screened on our patio in Melbourne! 

BAADDD shirts are available in all sizes: men's and women's S, M, L and male XL in black and white, and ladies S and M in pink. 

ICE CREAM CANDY shirts are available in all women's sizes in black and white, and S and M in pink.

Shirts are $30 EACH.  Please email us at hoofkake@gmail.com if your size isn't up and you would like it! xoxo
